node.text:
What marketing gaps can you fill with AI tools?

Here're some examples of questions you can ask yourself to determine what SaaS you can apply to your B2C business today:

- Which marketing aspect could use data analysis for better decision-making?
- What work takes you or your team hours implementing that could be done with AI marketing?
- How can the AI analysis help you communicate your campaign goals, discoveries, and improvements?
- Where could you improve your digital marketing efforts overall?

Answering these questions can help you identify which sort of marketing tasks you can lend over to an AI while increasing your productivity, ROI, and overall brand development.

In this article, we present our top 5 recommended tools for you to consider. Check out the link in bio to view them!
